<div class="well">
  <h4>As many columns or rows may be added as liked.</h4>
  <li><b>Adding another row</b> should be <b>adding a new patient/drug entity</b></li>
  <li><b>Adding another column</b> should be <b>adding another timeslot</b></li>
  <li>The timeslots should be in order, from earliest to latest.</li>
  <li>No duplicate DataGroup names are allowed. In the above examples, each row represents a different patient/drug 'data group', where P1 means 'patient 1 for drug X', etc.</li>
</div>